title: Gorgeous young mom drops tot-son with babysitter, disappears.  HELP FIND Prisma Denise Reyes
itunes:title: Gorgeous young mom drops tot-son with babysitter, disappears.  HELP FIND Prisma Denise Reyes
description:
26-year-old Denise Prisma Reyes, disappears in Texas just a short time before she was supposed to pick up her young son from the babysitter. With few clues, her family is now offering a reward for information.

Dan Fuchs, Reyes stepfather, joins Nancy with the latest in the search for his loved one.

Nancy's expert panel weighs in:

Leigh Egan: CrimeOnline investigative reporter

Ashley Willcott: Judge and Trial Attorney

Jeff Cortese: Former FBI supervisory special agent

David Mack: Syndicated Radio Host

Caryn Stark: Psychologist

Robyn Walensky: CrimeOnline investigative reporter
